question, how do we cure it?

00:17:46.390 --> 00:17:49.710 align:middle line:84%
And the answer is
it's self care.

00:17:49.710 --> 00:17:51.690 align:middle line:84%
So when we take great
care of ourselves

00:17:51.690 --> 00:17:55.840 align:middle line:84%
through mind, body, spiritual
care, through health, wealth,

00:17:55.840 --> 00:17:58.940 align:middle line:84%
and relationship care,
through diet, exercise,

00:17:58.940 --> 00:18:04.560 align:middle line:84%
and conscious
absorption of knowledge

00:18:04.560 --> 00:18:06.960 align:middle line:84%
and contributing
back to others--

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:09.780 align:middle line:84%
when you have that level
of self care in your life,

00:18:09.780 --> 00:18:15.955 align:middle line:84%
your insecurities don't
have any control over you.

00:18:15.955 --> 00:18:17.580 align:middle line:84%
They can't keep up
with you when you're

00:18:17.580 --> 00:18:19.990 align:middle line:90%
taking great care of yourself.

00:18:19.990 --> 00:18:24.690 align:middle line:84%
And so these self care
rituals, I respect them.

00:18:24.690 --> 00:18:30.570 align:middle line:84%
And anytime I'm in
a dark place, or I'm

00:18:30.570 --> 00:18:33.760 align:middle line:84%
