00:18:40.530 --> 00:18:44.240 align:middle line:84%
and yet how many
times do I forget it.

00:18:44.240 --> 00:18:49.080 align:middle line:84%
And so that's one of the
reasons why I'm here--

00:18:49.080 --> 00:18:54.010 align:middle line:84%
is to let human beings
