00:40:05.930 --> 00:40:07.250 align:middle line:90%
You can't be sad.

00:40:07.250 --> 00:40:08.180 align:middle line:90%
You can't be this.

00:40:08.180 --> 00:40:09.830 align:middle line:90%
You can't be that--

00:40:09.830 --> 00:40:10.630 align:middle line:90%
it bottles up.

