00:44:31.870 --> 00:44:34.980 align:middle line:84%
There's a great book called
"Mind Sculpting," that I love.

00:44:34.980 --> 00:44:40.280 align:middle line:90%
And it's rehearsal.

00:44:40.280 --> 00:44:42.030 align:middle line:84%
Because the mind can't
tell the difference

00:44:42.030 --> 00:44:44.127 align:middle line:90%
between imagination and reality.

00:44:44.127 --> 00:44:45.960 align:middle line:84%
Specifically, mine can't
tell the difference

00:44:45.960 --> 00:44:48.980 align:middle line:90%
