differently than if you

00:45:18.720 --> 00:45:21.220 align:middle line:90%
didn't do the mental rehearsal.

00:45:21.220 --> 00:45:26.290 align:middle line:84%
And so when I get up on
stage, like I did today,

00:45:26.290 --> 00:45:28.650 align:middle line:84%
