And I watched you write
down notes that I'm sharing.

00:45:48.410 --> 00:45:54.250 align:middle line:84%
And I see you have this
shift of experience.

00:45:54.250 --> 00:45:58.360 align:middle line:84%
And I've convinced myself, long
before I get on that stage,

00:45:58.360 --> 00:46:02.980 align:middle line:84%
