laugh, but you cried.

00:46:02.980 --> 00:46:07.040 align:middle line:90%
And you shift the way you think.

00:46:07.040 --> 00:46:09.110 align:middle line:90%
You rethought your life.

00:46:09.110 --> 00:46:11.740 align:middle line:84%
And so when I get
up on stage or I

00:46:11.740 --> 00:46:17.410 align:middle line:84%
