we know how this ends.

00:46:29.300 --> 00:46:30.100 align:middle line:90%
It's beautiful.

00:46:30.100 --> 00:46:31.570 align:middle line:90%
Let's do this.

00:46:31.570 --> 00:46:36.460 align:middle line:84%
And that's what gives me
such great advantages.

00:46:36.460 --> 00:46:39.490 align:middle line:84%
Visualization is so
a part of my life

00:46:39.490 --> 00:46:43.570 align:middle line:84%
