00:48:01.180 --> 00:48:03.140 align:middle line:84%
I'm not getting
up for my spouse.

00:48:03.140 --> 00:48:05.750 align:middle line:84%
I'm not just getting up
for my extended family,

00:48:05.750 --> 00:48:07.480 align:middle line:84%
and my friends,
and my customers.

00:48:07.480 --> 00:48:09.620 align:middle line:90%
I'm getting up for the world.

00:48:09.620 --> 00:48:10.580 align:middle line:90%
Is that cocky?

00:48:10.580 --> 00:48:12.010 align:middle line:90%
Maybe.

00:48:12.010 --> 00:48:13.340 align:middle line:90%
But can I back it?

00:48:13.340 --> 00:48:14.450 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:48:14.450 --> 00:48:17.330 align:middle line:84%
You know the difference
between arrogance and cocky?

00:48:17.330 --> 00:48:19.580 align:middle line:90%
Cocky person can back it up.

00:48:19.580 --> 00:48:22.190 align:middle line:84%
And I backed up
time and time again

00:48:22.190 --> 00:48:25.340 align:middle line:84%
with how I've lived
my life, that I'm here

00:48:25.340 --> 00:48:29.300 align:middle line:84%
to rid the world of
insecurity by using myself

00:48:29.300 --> 00:48:32.840 align:middle line:84%
as the laboratory and
sharing my findings.

00:48:32.840 --> 00:48:36.810 align:middle line:84%
So when I wake up and my eyes
