Sometimes, it's just
getting a message

00:51:48.070 --> 00:51:51.350 align:middle line:84%
from a complete stranger
on Facebook saying,

00:51:51.350 --> 00:51:52.850 align:middle line:90%
I was having a tough day.

00:51:52.850 --> 00:51:57.380 align:middle line:84%
And I watched your
silly dance party video,

00:51:57.380 --> 00:51:59.810 align:middle line:84%
and you turned it
all around for me.

00:51:59.810 --> 00:52:01.880 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

